sentences: Lena Nymark (born 6 November 1980 in Ålesund, Norway) is a Norwegian jazz singer and music teacher raised on the island Sula, south of Ålesund.
Nymark's debut solo album Beautiful Silence was released in 2014.
Previously Nymark participated in the electro-acoustic trio DinoSau.
